Riedel Bottle Cleaner Beads
List.Description: It just got easier to clean your valuable decanters with metallic cleaning beads from Riedel.  These tiny stainless steel pellets remove all dirt, residue, sediment and stains from inside the decanter.  Just fill the vessel half way up with water, add the pellets, and swish around for about two minutes.  That's it!  When you're done, carefully empty the contents into a mesh strainer, rinse the pellets, dry them, and use them again and again.

List.Name: Pioneers of California Wine
List.Description:
A handful of wineries and their entrepreneurial founders paved the way for the California wine industry as we know it today. This wine gift trio pays tribute to those pioneers of California wine with three exemplary varietals from the wineries that helped to place them on the California wine map.

Wine Gift Trio Includes:

  • Buena Vista Carneros Chardonnay
    On the palate, the wine's crisp acidity complements the intense flavors of rich apple, pear and vibrant peaches before culminating in a long, creamy finish that is typical of Carneros Chardonnay.

  • Raymond Napa Valley Reserve Cabernet Sauvignon
    This is a full-bodied Cabernet Sauvignon that boasts lots of volume and is rich and velvety with notes of dark fruit and black tea.

  • DeLoach Russian River Pinot Noir
    Delicate notes of anise and baking spices lace the fruit to unfold a rich palate of black cherries supported by medium fine-grain tannins.

  • Printed insert that describes the featured wines

    Due to the popularity of this gift, vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage.

List.Name: Lafite Around the World Red Wine Gift Trio
List.Description:
Also available: Caymus & More Gift Trio

The Lafite Rothschild name is recognized by wine collectors and enthusiasts around the world. With properties in multiple wine regions, Rothschild wines display attention to detail and exceptional quality. For this gift, we've selected Paradis Casseuil from Bordeaux, Château d'Aussières from the Languedoc and Los Vascos from Chile.

Wine Gift Trio Includes:

  • Bordeaux: Paradis Casseuil
    Fresh, fruity flavors and floral aromas. In the mouth, the attack is rounded and hearty with prolonged red fruit and wild berries. This wine can be appreciated now or kept for a few years when it will have reached its peak.

  • Languedoc: Château d'Aussières
    Very dark, almost black, garnet color. The nose is subtle but has superb depth and perfectly integrated, almost imperceptible woodiness with a hint of blackcurrants. a wine of density and exceptional finesse.

  • Chile: Los Vascos Reserve Cabernet Sauvignon
    A benchmark for elegance and finesse in Chile. The wine is characterized by the complexity and persistence of its bouquet of cherries and blackcurrants, strawberries, raspberries and plums, with notes of bay leaves and black pepper. A delicious, exciting wine, with great density and harmony.

  • Greet Sheet with descriptions of the three featured wineries and recipe pairings for each wine. The description cards and recipes are perforated as 4x5 index cards to be torn off for future reference.

    Due to the popularity of this gift, vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage.

Riedel 'O' Decanter
List.Description:
Riedel decanters combine sophistication and elegance with optimal shapes for aeration. Decanting old wines, just a few moments before they are served, helps to ensure that the wine's clarity and brilliance are not obscured by any deposit that may have developed over time. Decanting young wines several hours before they are served gives the wine a chance to bloom and attain a stage of development that normally requires years of aging.

The Riedel 'O' Decanter was designed to complement Riedel's casual 'O" wine tumblers. This decanter has a deep punt in the base that assists with one-handed pouring. The wide, elliptical mouth allows for a drip-free pour. The decanter stands 8 7/8" high and holds 34 1/2 oz. Made from 24% lead crystal.

Wine sold separately.
